<L>__{exterior honeydripper lounge night}
<A>__{we hear piano music as we crane down toward the honeydripper lounge, a ramshackle wooden roadhouse at a rural crossroads. blue colored light bulbs (a few broken) flick on and off erratically around the honeydripper sign as we track toward and then through it on the way to the entrance, catching up with lonnie and scratch. the boys step under the door light, frantic with insects, and go up on their toes to peek in through a window }
